OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,7,F"apologises" for the delay in
OL,8,Fpublishing a report into Nottingham
OL,9,FHopsital Trust's maternity services.
OL,11,FThe healthcare watchdog investigated
OL,12,FNottingham City Hospital and the
OL,13,FQueens Medical Centre maternity
OL,14,Fservices in June last year after
OL,15,Freceiving concerning information from
OL,16,Fstaff.
