OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,FThe watchdog blamed its new computer
OL,7,Fsystems for the delay and said it's
OL,8,Ftaking "urgent steps to ensure that
OL,9,Finspection reports are published in a
OL,10,Fmuch more timely manner."
OL,12,FBoth services remain rated as
OL,13,F"requires improvement" after seven
OL,14,Fbreaches of regulation in safe care
OL,15,Fwere found.
OL,17,FAt Queen's Medical Centre, the CQC
OL,18,Ffound three breaches regarding
OL,19,Finfection control procedures,
OL,20,Fequipment safety, and medicines
OL,21,Fmanagement and storage.
