OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,FIt also found four breaches relating
OL,7,Fto infection control procedures,
OL,8,Fequipment safety, medicines and
OL,9,Fexpressed milk storage at Nottingham
OL,10,FCity Hospital.
OL,12,FThe CQC said there were "some
OL,13,Fimprovements" in care but "more
OL,14,Fchanges were needed to improve the
OL,15,Fstandard of care women, people using
OL,16,Fthe services, and their babies were
OL,17,Freceiving."
