OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,FNottingham City Hospital's overall
OL,7,Frating remains as "good" and Queen's
OL,8,FMedical Centre remains rated as
OL,9,F"requires improvement."
OL,11,FHelen Rawlings, Interim Director of
OL,12,FNetwork Operations in the Midlands,
OL,13,Fsaid: "When we inspected maternity
OL,14,Fservices at Nottingham University
OL,15,FHospitals NHS Trust in June and July
OL,16,Flast year, we found some improvements
OL,17,Fhad been made, although more changes
OL,18,Fwere needed to improve the standard of
OL,19,Fcare women, people using the services,
OL,20,Fand their babies were receiving.
