OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,F"Prior to the inspection, we were
OL,7,Fconcerned by information we received
OL,8,Ffrom whistleblowers, who expressed
OL,9,Ftheir concerns regarding both services.
OL,11,F"In both maternity services, people
OL,12,Ffelt safe when they were on the wards
OL,13,Fand in the labour suite. However, a
OL,14,Fnumber of people told us that there
OL,15,Fwere delays with the induction
OL,16,Fprocesses.
OL,18,FAlso, staff weren't always available
OL,19,Fif they needed any help or support.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
