OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,F"It was positive to hear that staff
OL,7,Ftreated people well and with kindness
OL,8,Fand compassion.
OL,10,F"One person at Nottingham City
OL,11,FHospital told us that staff were
OL,12,Fthoughtful and caring, they felt
OL,13,Flistened to and staff communicated
OL,14,Fwith them in a way which they could
OL,15,Funderstand.
