OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,F"There were clear signs that the
OL,7,Fculture was improving, however, some
OL,8,Fstaff felt there was a lack of
OL,9,Funderstanding of individual roles and
OL,10,Fresponsibilities, which led to staff
OL,11,Fnot understanding each other's
OL,12,Fchallenges.
OL,14,F"However, leaders were working to
OL,15,Faddress the negative culture that
OL,16,Fremained in some areas. This is
OL,17,Fimportant as staff's ability to speak
OL,18,Fup when things aren't working has an
OL,19,Fimpact on people's care.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
