OL,3,CWatchdog apologies for delayed report
OL,4,Cinto Nottingham maternity services
OL,6,F"It's clear that staff and leaders had
OL,7,Fworked hard to make some improvements,
OL,8,Fand since the inspection last year,
OL,9,Fleaders have assured us that further
OL,10,Fimprovements have been made.
OL,12,F"We'll continue to monitor the trust
OL,13,Fto ensure that more changes are made
OL,14,Fand embedded so women, people using
OL,15,Fthe service, and their babies receive
OL,16,Fthe safe care they have a right to
OL,17,Fexpect."
